Reposted from @alli.leigh.p Pic from @djcavano Please stop with the wide variety of masks: homemade, bandanas, ski masks, even surgical or N95s. You are wearing and using them incorrectly and if they weren’t already ineffective (the majority of the ones I see people wearing) they are made ineffective by your practices. Therefore all it serves to do is control you and give you and others a false sense of security. Only wear if you are REQUIRED to and even then...PUSH BACK because it’s ridiculous!! Enjoy that fresh Spring air people!! .
